snippet.title: Infobells - Hindi
snippet.description:
Infobells Interactive Solutions is a multi-faceted E-Learning firm, engaged in publishing and marketing of Interactive Educational & Edutainment video content, covering a wide variety of categories like Children Rhymes, Animated Stories, Kids Education, Reference, Lifestyle, Self Improvement, CBT's etc.

Infobells showed a natural interest towards the Hindi language and produced a one of a kind 3D character animated "Favourite Hindi Rhymes"-  A superb collection of fun filled traditional Hindi Rhymes.
